Subject: [PATCH 1/2] fix(database): Checkpoint-Database-Fixed
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Schema fixes:
- Removed duplicate root-level schema.prisma (backend/prisma/schema.prisma is authoritative)
- Updated binaryTargets: added 'windows' for Windows 10 compatibility
- Added extra indexes on refresh_tokens (idx_refresh_tokens_user, idx_refresh_tokens_hash)
- Corrected DateTime? to DateTime for non-nullable timestamp fields
- Added named relations (SaleCashier, TransferFromBranch, etc.)
- Cleaned inline comments from field definitions

Migrations:
- Created backend/prisma/migrations/20260614000000_init/migration.sql
- Migration matches live DB (_prisma_migrations already records this migration)
- All 24 tables covered, 9 enums, 71 indexes

Seed data (scripts/init.sql):
- Fixed admin password hash (was invalid bcrypt, now verified: Admin@1234 ✅)
- Seed includes: 2 branches, 1 admin, 8 categories, 8 brands, 3 suppliers,
  20 products (SP-001..SP-020), 40 inventory entries (MAIN + WH01)

New file:
- scripts/seed.sql: standalone seed file, safe to re-run (ON CONFLICT DO UPDATE)
  Run after init.sql on a fresh database:
  psql -h 127.0.0.1 -U erp_user -d erp_pos -f scripts/seed.sql

Verification results:
- All 24 tables exist in live PostgreSQL 16 database
- All 8 login-flow SQL queries execute successfully
- admin user: ACTIVE, correct bcrypt hash, branch=MAIN
- refresh_tokens table: functional (insert/revoke tested)
- audit_logs table: functional (insert tested)
- 20 products, 40 inventory rows, 3 suppliers seeded
- No frontend changes, no API changes, no refactoring
